  "title": "Tapping for the fear of losing what you gain",
  "subtitle": "A five-minute script for releasing the expectation that good fortune won't last.",
  "excerpt": "A five-minute tapping practice from Day 19 of the MONEY program. The script targets the pattern of tensing up when money arrives, expecting hidden setbacks, and believing wealth will slip away as soon as it lands.",
  "type": "PRACTICE",
  "sourceNotes": "Adapted from Day 19 of MONEY: A 12-Week Tapping Program (Rebecca J Page, 2025), \"End 'I'll lose it if I gain it' worry.\" Tapping framework: Gary Craig's Emotional Freedom Technique (EFT), in use since the mid-1990s, building on Roger Callahan's Thought Field Therapy.",
  "body": {
